main_body:
Regulation (EC) No 2406/96 is amended as follows:
1. in Article 3(1)(a), the following indent is added:
‘— Sprat (Sprattus sprattus)’;
2. Annexes I and II are amended as follows:
(a) in Annex I, point B (Bluefish), the word ‘sprat’ is added;
(b) in Annex II, the entry set out in the text in the Annex to this Regulation is added.
